doctype 5
html
  head
    title Monster on X
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    link(href='bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css', rel='stylesheet', media='screen')
    link(href='monsteronx.css', rel='stylesheet', media='screen')
  body
    //- Head
    div(class='container')
      div(class='row')
        div(class='col-md-12 text-center')
          h1 Monster on X
    div(class='rulers')
      hr(class='light-red')
      hr(class='dark-red')
    //- Middlepart
    div(class='middelpart')
      div(class='container')
        div(class='row')
          div(class='col-md-6')
            p As a participant of Monster on X I should meet nice people, have a beer with them and learn new things
          div(class='col-md-6')
            p Reminder: Don't forget - every last Thursday in month - 7pm. Next Meetups asdjalksdjalskdj.
    div(class='rulers')
      hr(class='grey')
    //- About
    div(class='aboutpart')
      div(class='container')
        div(class='row')
          div(class='col-md-12 text-center')
            h2 About
            p Monster on X, formely Monster on Rails, was originally founded as Ruby on Rails Usergroup MÃ¼nster. Since then are many corresponding technologies around and we are dealing with many topics like Ruby, Ruby on Rails, Node.js, Sinatra, Software-Architecture, Frontend Performance, JavaScript in general, backbone.js, ember.js, angularJS and more. Besides we are talking about enterprise and startup architectures and DBS. Usually we meet monthly.
    div(class='rulers')
      hr(class='dark-red')
    //- Recent Topics
    div(class='topicspart')
      div(class='container')
        div(class='row')
          div(class='col-md-12')
            h2(class='text-center') Recent Topics
        div(class='row')
          include recenttopics/topics
      div(class='rulers')
        hr(class='light-grey')
      //- Upcoming Topics
      div(class='container')
        div(class='row')
          div(class='col-md-12')
            h2(class='text-center') Upcoming Topics
            iframe(src='https://trello.com/b/3u7oz7Xw/open-monster-x-board')
            a(class='', href='https://trello.com/b/3u7oz7Xw/open-monster-x-board') see whats coming Next
    div(class='rulers')
      hr(class='light-grey')
    //- Partners
    div(class='container')
      div(class='row')
        div(class='col-md-12 text-center')
          h2 Partners
          include partners/partners
      div(class='row')
        div(class='col-md-12 text-center')
          img(src='http://www.monstergrill.io/img/made-with-love-in-muenster.png')
    //- JavaScripts
    script(src='http://code.jquery.com/jquery.js')
    script(src='bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js')